{
  "texts": [
    "And give a penalty to the short predicted sentences as below in Eqs.",
    "(1) and (2).",
    "where BP is the brevity penalty, which is a correction factor that reduces the score for translations that are shorter than the reference translations.",
    "N is the maximum n-gram size considered in the evaluation.",
    "p_1, p_2, …, p_n are the n-gram precisions, which are calculated as the ratio of the number of matching n-grams in the machine-translated output to the total number of n-grams in the output."
  ]
}